    <sec id="Sec9">
      <title>Goodness of fitting (GOF)</title>
      <p>To display the goodness of fitting (GOF), the simulations is performed using the estimated parameters. For the simulation of the 1S mode, <italic>m</italic> background bins and <italic>n</italic> signal bins were randomly sampled according to <italic>π</italic><sub><italic>s</italic></sub>, where <italic>m</italic>+<italic>n</italic>=<italic>T</italic>. The background read count of <italic>T</italic> bins were generated from the background distribution <inline-formula id="IEq24"><alternatives><tex-math id="M49">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
